"last_modified": 1673491726, "replies": 80, "id": 908354}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 195866, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340", "stars": 3679, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 447838, "username": "overthemoon", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/overthemoon", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/10d6/900c/447838_mini.png?m=1589448128", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/10d6/900c/447838_normal.png?m=1589448128", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/10d6/900c/447838_large.png?m=1589448128", "created": 1571467471, "last_modified": 1589448128}, "last_reply_by": "fengleiyidao", "last_touched": 1673506712, "title": "相亲送女孩子什么见面礼好", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/908322", "created": 1673487955, "deleted": 0, "content": "第一次约相亲对象出来，一般去哪好，要不要送见面礼，一般送啥好", "content_rendered": "<p>第一次约相亲对象出来，一般去哪好，要不要送见面礼，一般送啥好</p>\n", "last_modified": 1673487955, "replies": 79, "id": 908322}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3cef/96dc/949_large.png?m=1614702882", "name": "nas", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3cef/96dc/949_normal.png?m=1614702882", "title": "NAS", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/nas", "topics": 893, "footer": "", "header": "关于网络存储设备的讨论", "title_alternative": "NAS", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3cef/96dc/949_mini.png?m=1614702882", "stars": 1318, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 949, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"id": 291702, "username": "wzhpro", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/wzhpro", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1f35/e609/291702_mini.png?m=1662432611", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1f35/e609/291702_normal.png?m=1662432611", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1f35/e609/291702_large.png?m=1662432611", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1f35/e609/291702_xlarge.png?m=1662432611", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1f35/e609/291702_xlarge.png?m=1662432611", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1f35/e609/291702_xlarge.png?m=1662432611", "created": 1518415396, "last_modified": 1662432611}, "last_reply_by": "ohmyself", "last_touched": 1673506868, "title": "想买一个性能强一点的 nas，求推荐", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/908232", "created": 1673434643, "deleted": 0, "content": "## 现状\r\n\r\n目前在用 HP GEN 10 （非 plus ）低配版 + UNRAID ，略显性能不足\r\n\r\n## 需求\r\n- 存储小于 4TB 的数据，目前在用 2*4TB 红盘\r\n- 数据需要保障安全性（ raid1 ，或软 raid ）\r\n- 跑 5 ～ 10 个 Docker ，如 syslog 、transmission 、mysql 等\r\n- 启 2 ～ 3 个 linux 虚拟机，1 个 Windows 虚拟机，做一些系统相关的实验，需要硬件直通等功能，最好 intel 平台\r\n- 懒得折腾，不想自己组装\r\n- 尽可能省电，最好是低功耗 CPU\r\n\r\n总结下来就是 2 盘位的高性能 nas\r\n\r\n## 市面产品调研\r\n\r\n本人孤陋寡闻，只了解了一些自己已知的产品，但都不满足需求\r\n\r\n| 产品 | 调研结果 |\r\n| ------ | ------ |\r\n| 群晖、威联通 | 略贵，且性能不行 |\r\n| NUC 华尔街峡谷 | 不支持 3.5 HDD ，且不能装 2 块硬盘 |\r\n| NUC 飞龙峡谷 | 不支持 3.5 HDD ，但可以装 2 个 nvme ssd ，只是容量会小一点。如果折腾一下的话可以插个 pcie 的 sata 卡来带 3.5 HDD 。如果实在找不到合适的准备就买这款 |\r\n| 小米 mini 主机 | 只支持 1 个 nvme ssd |\r\n| 某宝上的工控机 | 某些型号可以有 2 个 sata 接口，但是后续扩展性比较差 |\r\n\r\n## 请大家指点\r\n\r\n感谢", "content_rendered": "<h2>现状</h2>\n<p>目前在用 HP GEN 10 （非 plus ）低配版 + UNRAID ，略显性能不足</p>\n<h2>需求</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>存储小于 4TB 的数据，目前在用 2*4TB 红盘</li>\n<li>数据需要保障安全性（ raid1 ，或软 raid ）</li>\n<li>跑 5 ～ 10 个 Docker ，如 syslog 、transmission 、mysql 等</li>\n<li>启 2 ～ 3 个 linux 虚拟机，1 个 Windows 虚拟机，做一些系统相关的实验，需要硬件直通等功能，最好 intel 平台</li>\n<li>懒得折腾，不想自己组装</li>\n<li>尽可能省电，最好是低功耗 CPU</li>\n</ul>\n<p>总结下来就是 2 盘位的高性能 nas</p>\n<h2>市面产品调研</h2>\n<p>本人孤陋寡闻，只了解了一些自己已知的产品，但都不满足需求</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>产品</th>\n<th>调研结果</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>群晖、威联通</td>\n<td>略贵，且性能不行</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>NUC 华尔街峡谷</td>\n<td>不支持 3.5 HDD ，且不能装 2 块硬盘</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>NUC 飞龙峡谷</td>\n<td>不支持 3.5 HDD ，但可以装 2 个 nvme ssd ，只是容量会小一点。如果折腾一下的话可以插个 pcie 的 sata 卡来带 3.5 HDD 。如果实在找不到合适的准备就买这款</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>小米 mini 主机</td>\n<td>只支持 1 个 nvme ssd</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>某宝上的工控机</td>\n<td>某些型号可以有 2 个 sata 接口，但是后续扩展性比较差</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table><h2>请大家指点</h2>\n<p>感谢</p>\n", "last_modified": 1673434774, "replies": 63, "id": 908232}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_large.png?m=1650127281", "name": "share", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_normal.png?m=1650127281", "title": "分享发现", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/share", "topics": 37170, "footer": "", "header": "分享你看到的好玩的，有信息量的，欢迎从这里获取灵感。", "title_alternative": "Share", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_mini.png?m=1650127281", "stars": 5142, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 16, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 359033, "username": "huhexian", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/huhexian", "website": "eirms.com", "twitter": "huhexian", "psn": "", "github": "huhexian", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "keep reading.", "bio": "个人博客：https://eirms.com", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/dc75b1021b41486d062ff0285fb94749?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/dc75b1021b41486d062ff0285fb94749?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/dc75b1021b41486d062ff0285fb94749?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1540637021, "last_modified": 1673433536}, "last_reply_by": "rocododd", "last_touched": 1673503566, "title": "送大家一个小小的新年礼物，定制微信红包封面", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/908226", "created": 1673433615, "deleted": 0, "content": "前天微信公众号官方给我发通知，我在 2022 年创作了 31